{%- comment -%}
Pixels / GTM placeholder snippet.
Usage:
- Edit this file to paste your pixel snippets (Meta / TikTok / GA4).
- Then include in layout/theme.liquid:
  - in <head>: {% render 'pixels' %}
  - or for body tags move parts into appropriate places.
Notes:
- For the quick start below, replace YOUR_META_PIXEL_ID, YOUR_TIKTOK_PIXEL_ID, YOUR_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID.
{%- endcomment -%}

